{"tid":564655,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"某日本中學男生可穿裙","createTime":"2018-02-18T08:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T12:35:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":19,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fb471fe8587c7370733ea29ee853634cb5bf9f87","tid":564655,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:34:02.000Z","msg":"近日，日本一所初中打破了僅有女生穿裙子的常規，使其學校的男生也有了穿短裙的機會。這所學校位於日本千葉縣，名為柏市立柏中學。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/253846_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F253846_1.jpg&h=7b46ef05&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/technology/player?newsId=253846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ftechnology%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D253846&d=gf5Gdp6S7239pWTH0YeD2eI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=89bdee18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ftechnology%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D253846&h=7b377af8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/technology/player?newsId=253846</a>"},{"pid":"6441d71914931345729f574f8ed02b39f655b175","tid":564655,"uid":1886,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"據了解，今年的4月份，柏市立柏中學正式開辦。此舉是考慮到學生中的LGBT群體，因此，學校討論決定採用西式校服外套，此款外套偏中性。而校服的下裝和配飾則由學生自己喜好搭配。因此，學校也允許男生穿裙子。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/253846_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F253846_2.jpg&h=f5c9e8e6&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n日本的初中男生所穿的校服是立領西服，而女生則是穿水手服。不過，該校的討論委員會的成員經過思考後，他們認為校服應考慮到LGBT群體的感受。於是學校才做出該項決定。學生統一穿中性風格的校服，即校服上衣是西式校服外套，而下裝則可以根據學生的喜好，自由選擇西裝褲或短裙。"},{"pid":"954fc7bd30b1b0c9c9e5b045842d12dcd2ee592a","tid":564655,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:34:54.000Z","msg":"此消息傳出後，日本網民對此提出了疑惑：「男生們真的需要穿裙子嗎？」「男生穿了裙子該去哪個廁所呢？」對此，教委也作出回應，他們表示會讓學生來做出校服的選擇權;具體是否照此實行，還要等開學以後再做處理。"},{"pid":"099397e99d38785bc8b7543fd0bf17d11fb2ce87","tid":564655,"uid":1790,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"竟然會考慮埋LGBT嘅感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本仔啲思想拍得住英美歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e9819a0d80c51d8e0d5509e513dcf06da2b748","tid":564655,"uid":15739,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:52:25.000Z","msg":"男子高中生的日常"},{"pid":"6c9e0d971db055ec1bc1c4b0fe7104f33b47eecb","tid":564655,"uid":9489,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:56:12.000Z","msg":"男的也好.jpg"},{"pid":"57a07ac2fd14c821a1e4c583950e7a9183aea89b","tid":564655,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fc570b6a1c9bf217d72f9403b43a08d5b1a852","tid":564655,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"099397e99d38785bc8b7543fd0bf17d11fb2ce87","tid":564655,"uid":1790,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"竟然會考慮埋LGBT嘅感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本仔啲思想拍得住英美歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T01:08:45.000Z","msg":"日本咁多BL薔薇扶他動漫同埋腐男腐女，呢方面progressive啲好正常"},{"pid":"033050815e7f76820d2ec11a228f45fc9f74ee0c","tid":564655,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T01:12:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4146581852eba0602142ca8fb20cdb2688229334","tid":564655,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T01:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce89